<!-- STORY -->
<section class="story section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story__inner">
      <div class="story__text">
        <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">The Meaning<br/>Behind the Name.</h2>
        <p class="story__lead">"Derived from the concept of professional craftsmanship (Techne) and providing a 'Techo' — a roof of stability — we began with a vision to bridge the gap between complex technology and everyday utility."</p>
        <p>Techo Traders was founded on a belief that no industry exists in isolation. Digital systems need physical infrastructure. Physical delivery needs digital intelligence. Infrastructure needs innovative marketing to reach the people who need it most.</p>
        <p>That interconnected reality is what shaped the Techo Traders ecosystem: three subsidiaries, each world-class in their domain, each made stronger by their siblings.</p>
        <p>Today, Techo Traders stands as a diversified holding company — stable, forward-thinking, and committed to the long-term development of Sri Lanka's technology and logistics landscape.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story__timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-year">Founded</span>
            <h4>The Vision Begins</h4>
            <p>Techo Traders established with a core mandate: integrate technology across industries.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot timeline-dot--labs"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-year labs-accent">Techo Labs</span>
            <h4>The Digital Division Launches</h4>
            <p>Our web development and digital marketing arm begins serving clients across Sri Lanka.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot timeline-dot--connect"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-year connect-accent">Techo Connect</span>
            <h4>Manufacturing Begins</h4>
            <p>Antenna manufacturing facility established, serving telecom and broadcast sectors.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot timeline-dot--xpress"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-year xpress-accent">Techo Xpress</span>
            <h4>Logistics Division Launches</h4>
            <p>Courier and delivery operations begin, powered by tracking tech from Techo Labs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot timeline-dot--gold"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-year" style="color:var(--accent-gold)">Today</span>
            <h4>A Complete Ecosystem</h4>
            <p>Three companies, one vision — operating in synergy across Sri Lanka and expanding regionally.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

